<subSubSection pageId="43" pageNumber="322" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="43.[1458,2665,2775,3479]" pageId="43" pageNumber="322">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1461,1816,3288,3321]" pageId="43" pageNumber="322">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Threats to Marie’s Vole are unknown. There are reported populations protected in Anzihe Nature Reserve and Miyaluo Provincial Park.
</paragraph>
